reviewText:
Great concert from PBS
Great customer service
Takes me back to the good old days and with these Artist you can understand the lyrics and how there expressed and it's so refreshing.

Wonderful music written by the originals but not performed by them. Many younger imitation band members and lots of really poor lip syncing here....but the overall takeaway is huge walk down memory lane. Gotta love the oldies.....
I am so happy with this product. The video is great for oldies. Quality of video is good and music is great. Purchase experience was excellent. Would purchase from seller again.
